CREATE VIEW BUSINESS_RULES.COMPONENT_S_PSA_C_FACTCOMPONENT
AS

  SELECT 
    bo."Business Key for Hub Component",    -- Business Key for Hub Component
    bo."Business Key for Hub Release",      -- Business Key for Hub Release
    bo."Business Key for Hub Delivery",     -- Business Key for Hub Delivery
    bo."Total # Of Test Cases",             -- TCASES from Satellite Component > DBT_RULE > Test Metrics
    bo."Total Number of CREQ",              -- CREQS from Satellite Component > DBT_RULE > Test Metrics
    bo."Number of CREQ with Testcase",      -- CREQSWITHTRACETOTCASE from Satellite Component > DBT_RULE > Test Metrics
    bo.TCASE_PRO_CREQ,                    -- TCASE_PRO_CREQ from Satellite Component > DBT_RULE > Test Metrics
    bo.IMPLPTH                            -- IMPLPTH from Satellite Component > DBT_STAGE > Default of COMPONENT_METRIC_U_DBT_STAGE

  FROM BUSINESSOBJECTS.COMPONENT_S_PSA_C_FACTCOMPONENT bo
